        <section id="about-about">
            <div><h2>What is Quirk?</h2></div>
            <div><p class="p-text">Quirk Magazine is an online magazine designed by and for young women. Frustrated with the current selection of magazines that objectify women, Quirk Magazine serves to be an alternative option. We care about topics relevant to young women today, ranging from fashion to social issues. We celebrate creativity by sharing artistic endeavors of other women. We value honest stories and reflections that allow us to look at the world with a new perspective. Our hope is that this magazine will spur you to experience life with unrelenting curiosity.</p></div>
