                        <h2>Abi Koh</h2><p class="subtext">Founder and Editor</p><p class="p-text">Born in Singapore, Abi picked up an American accent while living in Kazakhstan as a little girl. She recently graduated from Northwestern University and is an ardent fan of design and front-end development. Abi loves obsessing over film, hugging people, receiving snail mail, drooling over the latest tech gadgets, and learning to see every cloud’s silver lining.</p>
                        <a href="https://twitter.com/hugyourlife" target="_blank"><p class="about-socialmedia">Twitter | @hugyourlife</p></a>
                        <a href="http://instagram.com/adventuresofabi" target="_blank"><p class="about-socialmedia">Instagram | adventuresofabi</p></a>
