                        <img src="http://i31.photobucket.com/albums/c358/TwilightMemory/blankbox.png" />
                        <h2>This could be you</h2>
                        <p class="p-text">Hello there! Quirk Magazine is looking for Main Contributors, Editors, Illustrators, and Photographers to help out as we grow. Main Contributors will produce content for Quirk on a regular basis. Editors will curate content and sift through submissions. Illustrators and Photographers will create visual imagery to go along with written articles. If interested, please email submissions@quirk-magazine.com.</p>
                        </td>
